    "OSSIM combines several open-source projects including Munin, Nagios, NFDump, OpenVAS, Snort, Suricata and TCPTrack.",
    "Elastic Security previously known as Elastic SIEM [52] is also a freely available solution for users.",
    "It is built on the Elastic Stack and is capable of detecting host and network-based complex security events using pre-built rules.",
    "Other features include vulnerability scanning, user authentication, and access control.",
    "The standard version of Elastic Security is free whereas Gold, Platinum and Enterprise versions are paid."
